==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Superable
<hw>Su"per*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>superabilis</ets>, from <ets>superare</ets> to go over, to
surmount, fr. <ets>super</ets> above, over.]</ety> <def>Capable of being
overcome or conquered; surmountable.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Antipathies are generally <qex>superable</qex> by a single
effort.</q> <rj><qau>Johnson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Su"per*a*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> --
<wf>Su"per*a*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Superabound</ent>⟦br⟧
